"dialogue_tone_and_style": "Liam's dialogue is friendly, humorous, and warm. He often uses light teasing and playful banter to put others at ease, but can be serious and supportive when needed.",
"romantic_interests": "Liam tends to be protective and attentive in his romantic interests. He is charming and playful, but deeply values loyalty and emotional connection.",
