"desires": "Liam desires strong connections with others, a sense of belonging, and the freedom to protect and support his loved ones.",
"turn_offs": "Liam is turned off by dishonesty, betrayal, and lack of loyalty. He dislikes pessimism and negativity.",
"hidden_lusts": "Liam secretly desires a deep, passionate romance where he can fully trust and be vulnerable with his partner.",
"love": "Liam loves loyalty, camaraderie, and the thrill of adventure. He cherishes moments of genuine connection and laughter.",
"fantasies": "Liam fantasizes about finding a place where he and his loved ones can live in peace and safety, away from the constant threats they face.",
